{"tid":383254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鮨 生日飯","createTime":"2017-09-01T10:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T11:19:06.000Z","uid":68965,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e109a3428f3bde524db2ed3f219cc274c05c3133","tid":383254,"uid":68965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:28:27.000Z","msg":"我上星期剛剛腸胃炎，個肚仲係脹脹的，今個星期四生日。佢話我生日比個 surprise我，同我去鮨(鮨係元朗一間最貴的日本料理餐廳),我同佢講，我仲未好番，個肚仲係唔掂。佢話要成個星期前 book,  去食貴野，梗係要特別日子去，你生日去啱哂！ 佢仲話，有無睇醫生呀？！ 見佢興致勃勃我唯有答佢，好啦，食完再去睇醫生。。。<br />\n<br />\n我明明係 like法國菜， 係，0係上年周年紀念去左。我無話唔 like日本野，但我腸胃炎，食中菜唔係好 d嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢愛自己多 d,  定愛我多 d. 我係咪好少氣。。。"},{"pid":"b7b4609237b6afc9ee4504dc795e3fe0f3b26e26","tid":383254,"uid":48021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"不如我代你同佢去，我想食好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae388ee207005c16113174da9b1e0c67bd21696","tid":383254,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如我代你同佢去，我想食好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe103683378956b1b46482e1f97706fe473bcf61","tid":383254,"uid":81995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"唔食慳返"}]}